Package edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tracker.model.project

Class Project

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_tracker.model.project.Project
public class Project extends Object
Contains all information about a project and holds controller methods that can add and remove both categories and tasks
Author:
Cole Hincken
